      • fromFragments

        public static BulkData fromFragments(Fragments bulkDataFragments)
        Returns a BulkData instance combining all BulkData instances in bulkDataFragments.
        Parameters:
        bulkDataFragments - Fragments instance with BulkData instances referencing individual fragments
        Returns:
        a BulkData instance combining all BulkData instances in bulkDataFragments.
        Throws:
        ClassCastException - if bulkDataFragments contains byte[]
        IllegalArgumentException - if bulkDataFragments contains URIs referencing different Resources or without Query Parameter length.

      • hasFragments

        public boolean hasFragments()
        Returns true, if the URI of this BulkData instance specifies offset and length of individual data fragments by Query Parameters offsets and lengths and therefore can be converted by toFragments(java.lang.String, int, org.dcm4che3.data.VR) to a Fragments instance containing BulkData instances referencing individual fragments.
        Returns:
        true if this BulkData instance can be converted to a Fragments instance by toFragments(java.lang.String, int, org.dcm4che3.data.VR)
